headline: Northern Trust Expands Partnership with Alchemy to Support Its New Special Opportunities Fund
summary: LONDON & GUERNSEY, February 18, 2025--Northern Trust (Nasdaq: NTRS) is expanding its relationship with Alchemy Partners, a private equity firm, to deliver asset servicing solutions for its latest special opportunities fund, Alchemy Special Opportunities Fund V L.P. (‘ASOF V’). ASOF V surpassed Alchemy’s fundraising target, securing total commitments of approximately EUR €1 billion (around US$1.03 billion).
